Your funny my friend. I don’t know if you have noticed but this is the server advertisement of Ultimaonline. I changed it so it looks more like a source release by removing anything that says join. I hope you do know that I am merely releasing the source based on what my fellow owners thought was best about the server… I hope your not directing that statement of stupidity towards me. The proof is on the forums of another website.If you wish, go look up Ultima-Rsps 317Webclient on google.

Note that Ultimaonline/ UltimaRsps are used interchangeably.
